Mick Moloney Irish-American Music and Popular Culture Field Recordings

"Irish Music Song and Dance: 2 of 2." End of afternoon World Music Institute Concert at Symphony Space, NYC. Musicians include:Mick Moloney (guitar, vocals, banjo), Eileen Ivers (fiddle), Donnie Golden (dance), Cathie Ryan (vocals), Seamus Egan (flute, banjo), Joanie Madden (flute) and unidentified conga drummer. Golden teaches a ceili dance. (Length: 00:10:00). aiamm1100C
